Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野告诉我的魔法咒语
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.28,0:01:44.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,让我找到了自我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.80,0:01:53.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,球技大赛首日便有天公作美
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.29,0:01:57.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家个个活力十足 满面笑容
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.73,0:02:00.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,身为学园长 深感欣慰
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.78,0:02:03.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家有精彩表现
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.24,0:02:08.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,通过比赛体会到公平竞争的可贵之处
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.34,0:02:14.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一年级棒球淘汰赛
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.55,0:02:19.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一班草莓群星VS二班胡萝卜战士 比赛开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.50,0:02:21.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全员 敬礼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.68,0:02:23.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.58,0:02:30.34,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（一局上半 胡萝卜战士攻）
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.77,0:02:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来吧 拓人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.39,0:02:36.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.88,0:02:38.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:40.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球 打者出局
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.72,0:02:42.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好嘞 来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.93,0:02:48.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人大人
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.40,0:02:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你怎么给敌人加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.51,0:02:51.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.90,0:02:52.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂喂
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.65,0:02:54.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油 加油
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.19,0:02:56.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很适合你啊 这顶帽子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.80,0:02:57.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.93,0:03:01.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学长们比网球吗 真优雅啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.87,0:03:02.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是她吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.04,0:03:05.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 是她
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.03,0:03:12.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没错 她就是人头狮
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.47,0:03:18.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对女生一律用正中央直球
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.99,0:03:23.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了 这家伙的球速应该不用担心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.26,0:03:31.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球 打者出局
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.30,0:03:33.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是拓人君哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.90,0:03:35.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很帅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.32,0:03:37.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去给你报仇
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.24,0:03:40.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞠野？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.91,0:03:52.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,450)\fnarial\fsp1}Katami Wakachita Yagadanse...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.09,0:03:50.70,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\pos(600,435)\fs22}（半身 分开了 矢是男性?）
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.90,0:03:58.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnarial\fsp1}Katami Wakachita...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.27,0:04:01.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnarial\fsp1}Yagadanse!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.28,0:04:13.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,场外全垒打啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天才运动少女
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.71,0:04:17.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不错吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.69,0:04:19.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们的代表大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.50,0:04:23.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你喜欢那型的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.38,0:04:24.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就追到手啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.02,0:04:26.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.05,0:04:31.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也有利于今后的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.92,0:04:39.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我说 武史那家伙不会真动心了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.71,0:04:46.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,四号吗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.88,0:04:59.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,支援够到位
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.95,0:05:05.21,note2,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,900)}（一局下半 草莓群星攻）
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.10,0:05:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上啊 拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.12,0:05:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拓人君好帅
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.71,0:05:16.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干掉他们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.87,0:05:18.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再大胆点
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.37,0:05:22.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要让外露的头发更有丰满感
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.71,0:05:24.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.10,0:05:27.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不用现在做吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.55,0:05:35.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们三人好久没这样在一起了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.58,0:06:00.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,安全上垒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:07.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.72,0:06:10.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讨厌 拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.54,0:06:14.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 拓人 我嫉妒你
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.27,0:06:17.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:18.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.46,0:06:20.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我没事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.81,0:06:23.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.68,0:06:24.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能站起来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.19,0:06:32.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.11,0:06:39.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比赛开始
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.79,0:06:43.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,坏球
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.85,0:06:46.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嘿 先行先行先行
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.51,0:06:48.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是水野的姐姐吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.92,0:06:51.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹在戏剧社承蒙关照了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.20,0:06:53.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,津名志拓人君
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.93,0:06:56.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你知道我的名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.64,0:06:59.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹经常提起你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.78,0:07:03.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,来
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.56,0:07:09.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,听说你们是双胞胎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.69,0:07:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是一模一样啊 阳鞠野同学
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.37,0:07:17.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,水野常提起你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.65,0:07:21.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连眼睛的颜色都一样漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.01,0:07:28.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,名副其实的牵制球啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.10,0:07:35.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球 打者出局
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.59,0:07:41.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,慢着
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.50,0:07:44.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这种时候不是应该在擦肩而过时说
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.97,0:07:48.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「球比预想中还快」之类的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.67,0:07:52.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您似乎很享受呢 夫人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.14,0:08:00.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油哦 四号打者
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.12,0:08:29.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.86,0:08:31.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.60,0:08:33.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好球 打者出局
